OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsafe online?               
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Technology companies will have to take 
OL,6, more action to keep children safe on   
OL,7, the internet, following the            
OL,8, introduction of the Online Safety Act. 
OL,10,FBut the new rules will not come in     
OL,11,Funtil 2025 - and critics say they do   
OL,12,Fnot go far enough.                     
OL,14,FChildren aged eight to 17 spend between
OL,15,Ftwo and five hours online per day,     
OL,16,Fresearch by the communications         
OL,17,Fregulator Ofcom suggests. Time spent   
OL,18,Fonline increases with age.             
